---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---
<BaseLayout title="The IT Guys – Practical Software & Technical Solutions" description="The IT Guys – Technical Solutions Inc. builds practical software and technology solutions from Kelowna, British Columbia.">
  <section class="hero">
    <p class="eyebrow">Kelowna, British Columbia</p>
    <h1>Technology should make life better.</h1>
    <p class="lede">We build software that helps people solve problems, stay connected, and enjoy life a little more.</p>
    <div class="hero-actions">
      <a class="button" href="/services/">Explore Services</a>
      <a class="button secondary" href="/company/">About the Company</a>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section split">
    <div>
      <p class="eyebrow">What we build</p>
      <h2>Practical software for mobile, web, and business.</h2>
    </div>
    <div class="copy">
      <p><strong>The IT Guys – Technical Solutions Inc.</strong> designs and develops software and technology solutions with a focus on reliability, simplicity, and long-term usefulness.</p>
      <p>Our current focus is mobile application development for iOS and Android, supported by the technical experience gained from nearly a decade of helping businesses solve real-world technology problems.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section">
    <p class="eyebrow">Focus areas</p>
    <h2>Software development, backed by real-world technical experience.</h2>
    <div class="grid">
      <article class="card">
        <span class="number">01</span>
        <h3>Mobile Applications</h3>
        <p>iOS and Android applications designed to be useful, approachable, and built for real users.</p>
      </article>
      <article class="card">
        <span class="number">02</span>
        <h3>Web Applications</h3>
        <p>Modern web-based tools and product experiences that are fast, responsive, and easy to maintain.</p>
      </article>
      <article class="card">
        <span class="number">03</span>
        <h3>Technical Solutions</h3>
        <p>Practical guidance and implementation shaped by years of supporting small and medium-sized businesses.</p>
      </article>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="band">
    <div class="section split">
      <div>
        <p class="eyebrow">Our mission</p>
        <h2>Reliable. Intuitive. Genuinely useful.</h2>
      </div>
      <div class="copy">
        <p>The IT Guys – Technical Solutions Inc. builds practical software and technology solutions that solve real-world problems.</p>
        <p>We believe software and technology should be reliable, intuitive, and genuinely useful.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section">
    <p class="eyebrow">How we think</p>
    <h2>Build things people enjoy using.</h2>
    <div class="grid two">
      <article class="card">
        <h3>Solve real problems</h3>
        <p>We focus on useful products, clear decisions, and practical outcomes rather than technology for its own sake.</p>
      </article>
      <article class="card">
        <h3>Design for the long term</h3>
        <p>Good software should be maintainable, understandable, and capable of evolving as needs change.</p>
      </article>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="cta">
    <div class="cta-inner">
      <h2>Let's build something useful.</h2>
      <p>Whether it is software, technology, or simply a better way to solve a problem, great solutions begin with understanding people's needs.</p>
      <a class="button" href="/contact/">Contact Us</a>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
